# Build after changes

After completing code or data changes in this project, **always run a build** before finishing:

```bash
npm run build:only
```

Use the full `npm run build` only when TypeScript checking or audio sync is also needed.

The publish step updates root `index.html`; skipping build leaves the standalone page stale.
